Requirements
 . Java 17+
 . Docker (for containerization)
 . Postman (for testing endpoints)

1.Clone the Repository:
git clone https://github.com/mini-zhu16/AH-Delivery.git
cd AH-assignment

2.Build the Application:
mvn clean package

3. Dockerizing the Application:
docker-compose build
docker-compose up

4. Open your browser and go to http://localhost:8080/h2-console/ and use the following connection settings:
. JDBC URL: jdbc:h2:mem:testdb
. User Name: sa
. Password: password

5. Go to postman and test the app using the available methods and endpoints
URL: http://localhost:8080/deliveries

6. Go to the database, run the query and check the data.